<h1>World Sim Game Documentation Change Summary</h1>
<p>Version: Ver0.2.6.a</p>
<p>Baseline: Ver0.2.6.</p>
<p>Status: patch release metadata and implementation summary.</p>
<h2>Generated Official Files</h2>
<ul>
<li><code>docs/official/game_universal_documentation_ver0.2.6.a.doc</code></li>
<li><code>docs/official/versions/game_doc_ver0.2.6.a.doc</code></li>
