</ul>
<h2>Patch Delta</h2>
<ul>
<li>Added a dedicated hydrology render dirty flag and map-space hydrology cache.</li>
<li>Moved river drawing out of the border layer.</li>
<li>Added river geometry preparation for smoother visual paths and river diagnostics.</li>
<li>Rendered rivers with hierarchy-aware width, terrain-aware muted colors, understroke, main stroke, highlights, and mouth caps.</li>
<li>Added Debug hydrology rows for river count, length, confluences, invalid uphill segments, dead ends, short rivers, and cache rebuild timing.</li>
<li>Carried forward the snapshot/UI and natural-region validation work already present in this patch workspace.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Validation</h2>
<ul>
<li><code>git diff --check</code> passed.</li>
<li><code>make</code> passed.</li>
</ul>
